      </div>
      <h1 class='title'>Post Office Closures</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1717WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1717ws' title='Col. 1717WS &mdash; HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1717WS' name='column_1717ws' href='#column_1717ws' rel='bookmark'>1717WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_389'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-barrett' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_389' title='Link to this speech by Mr John Barrett' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <span class='question_no'>11.</span>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-john-barrett" title="Mr John Barrett">John Barrett</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Trade and Industry how many urban post offices have closed in the last 12 months. [189180]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_390'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-gerry-sutcliffe' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_390' title='Link to this speech by Mr Gerry Sutcliffe' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-gerry-sutcliffe" title="Mr Gerry Sutcliffe">Mr. Sutcliffe</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">I understand from Post Office Ltd. that in financial year 2003&#x2013;04 there were a total of 1,129 urban post office closures, including 1,109 under the urban network reinvention programme. In the first quarter of this financial year, to the end of June, there were 246 urban post office closures. 206 of those closures were under the urban network reinvention programme.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_391'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-peter-pike' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_391' title='Link to this speech by Mr Peter Pike' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <span class='question_no'>14.</span>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-peter-pike" title="Mr Peter Pike">Mr. Pike</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Trade and Industry what recent representations she has received on the sub-post office urban closure programme. [189183]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_392'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-gerry-sutcliffe' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_392' title='Link to this speech by Mr Gerry Sutcliffe' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-gerry-sutcliffe" title="Mr Gerry Sutcliffe">Mr. Sutcliffe</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">DTI Ministers and officials regularly receive representations on a wide range of postal services issues, including the urban network reinvention programme.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_393'>  </a>
        <blockquote class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <cite class='member author entry-title unmatched-member'>Mr. Michael Jabez Foster</cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Trade and Industry how many Post Office branches have been proposed for closure by the Post Office under the Post Office reinvention programme; and how many have been subsequently confirmed for closure after the consultation process has been completed. [187843]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_394'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-gerry-sutcliffe' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_394' title='Link to this speech by Mr Gerry Sutcliffe' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-gerry-sutcliffe" title="Mr Gerry Sutcliffe">Mr. Sutcliffe</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">This is an operational matter for Post Office Ltd. and I have therefore asked the Chief Executive to reply to the hon. Member.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
